[Name] Inotify-Tools
[Summary] A C library and a set of command-line programs providing a simple interface to inotify.
[Description] inotify-tools is a C library and a set of command-line programs for Linux providing a simple interface to inotify. These programs can be used to monitor and act upon filesystem events. The programs are written in C and have no dependencies other than a Linux kernel supporting inotify.
